data.description: Open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, skylights, hardwood and tile floors. Kitchen with marble counter tops, breakfast bar and plenty of cabinet space. Deck off of dining opens to spacious back yard with hot tub and gazebo.  HOA includes indoor pool, gym, clubhouse, walking trails and much more. Custom owned ADT Alarm.  New HVAC unit this last year.  Solotube. Granite/Import Tile Bath. Hardwoods. Custom ceiling fan & chandeliers.  Electric skylight in kitchen.
